node.text:
I want to convey the real Osaka Street. This is Osaka. It is a city with a long history. I have humanity. Usually, we eat soul food and a lot of people come together to have fun conversations and quarrels.
Time is midnight.
But those days disappeared because of him.
Yes, "Corona virus".
Now the city is quiet because of this guy.
There are no tourists. The ones who are out there. But sometimes it's good. Go out in a cool car and meet friends after a long absence. I do not know when to meet again next time. Please be fine until then.
Many car events have also been canceled. The world is exhausted. Please watch the video and get well. Cars are not infected. For now, let's just contact the car.
⠀
Video: Lower Motion
⠀
